@node summary "SUMMARY"

   Item: SUMMARY
   
   Menu: PRINT/SUMMARY

   SHORTCUT  Current RCOMMAND 8. By Date 9. Range 0.


   CURRENT

   This will search through the #?.log file for all the Invoices
   that were issued today, this session.

   DATE

   You can enter a date. Invoicer will search through the #?.log file
   for all the Invoices that were issued on that date.

   RANGE

   You enter a range of dates for Invoicer to search for.

   FILTER   If you want a summary of just one customer.

You have the option of outputting to the Printer or Screen.

